CK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>)下跌1.9%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對穩健，思科系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CSCO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CSCO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CSCO-US</a>)上漲4.55%；默克藥廠(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRK:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRK\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRK-US</a>)上漲2.71%；耐吉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NKE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NKE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NKE-US</a>)上漲2.04%；安進(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMGN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMGN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMGN-US</a>)上漲1.72%；雪佛龍(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVX-US</a>)上漲1.5%。</p></section></main>",
